    {
      "description": "np0288_exskill_level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "行きますよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_exskill_level_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_exweapon_get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "こうして先生と一緒に避暑に来られて、とっても楽しいです！改めて……いつもありがとうございます、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_exweapon_get.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生とおでかけ！ですね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_formation_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "えへへっ、とっても楽しみです♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "わわわっ！？落ちちゃうかと思いました……えへへ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_formchange",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "じゃじゃーん！シュエリンです！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_formchange.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私、成長したみたいです！えっと……いいこと、なんですよね？あれ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_growup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "この姿になると、色々なことを考えちゃいます。身体は大きくなったけれど、果たして成長しているのか……あっ、なんだか感傷的になっちゃいましたね！今のは聞かなかったことに……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今の私は、期間限定の泡沫……。だからこそ、この時間を大切にしたいんです。先生とこうやって過ごす瞬間は、かけがえのない宝物ですから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "む……なんだか、また大きくなった気がします……。……えっ私、何か変なこと言いました？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今の私は、教官ではありません！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "なので…普段できないことを、い～っぱいしちゃいます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "大きくなるにつれて、体感時間が短くなっていくと聞きました。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "子供の時は、目に映るものがすべて新鮮で輝いていて…だから時間がゆっくりだったんです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_2_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今の私は身体は小さいですが、色々なことを知っているので――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_2_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_2_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "もしかしたら、同年代の他の子よりも、体感時間が短くなってるかもしれませんね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_2_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "着替えてきた「シュエリン」と一緒に行きたい場所、ありますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_3_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私は先生と一緒なら、どこでも良いですよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_3_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "水遊び、楽しいですね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "でも…本当は、先生と遊べるならなんでも嬉しいです！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "もしも私が溺れちゃったら…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "それが「ふり」だとしても、先生は助けに来てくれますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_lobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "なんとなく…そういうのに憧れちゃうだけです。本当にやったりはしませんよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_lobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_login_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "こんにちは！先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_login_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_login_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "「シュエリン」は、先生と遊びたいです！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_login_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_login_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "はい！「シュエリン」ですよ！水着に着替えてきちゃいました♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_login_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_login_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "どうでしょう、先生？可愛いですか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_login_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "トロピカルフルーツが食べたくなってきました……先生はどんなフルーツが好きですか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生は何をして遊びたいですか？私は……おんぶしてもらいたいです！それから……えへへっ、秘密です！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "小さい頃、水遊びに熱中しすぎて夏風邪を引いちゃったことがあるんです。……って、「今」も小さかったですね。とにかく！先生も夏風邪には注意するんですよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今の私が経験する出来事は、過去の上書きになるんでしょうか？でもきっと、違いますよね。だって、こうして過ごしている全ての時間が、新しい思い出になっているんですから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今日、私の誕生日なんです！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生、誕生日プレゼントはなんですか？…ふふっ、子供はプレゼントがあるものだと思っているんですよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_birthday_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "なので――今日は、いっぱい甘やかしてくださいね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_birthday_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_birthday_player_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お誕生日おめでとうございます、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_birthday_player_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "…今度、私の誕生日も、お祝いしてくださいね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生！お菓子ってありますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "トリックオアトリートで持っていかれちゃう前に、いくつか食べておきたくて…！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_newyear_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "年が明けましたね。あけましておめでとうございます、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_newyear_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_newyear_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "シュエリンはまた一つ、お姉さんになりました！…この姿で言うのは、なんだか不思議な気分ですね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_newyear_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "クリスマスですよ、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "この一年、私は「良い子」だったでしょうか？先生サンタが来てくれたら…嬉しいです♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_defeat_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_defeat_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_defeat_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_defeat_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_in_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "小さくても、できるんですよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_in_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "任せてください！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_victory_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "えへへ、先生、見てました？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_victory_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0288_tactic_victory_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "いってきます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/np0288_tactic_victory_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0288_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ！えへへ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E9%9B%AA%E7%8E%B2/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/NP0288_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
